BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION

[`{[$a] \choose [$d]} - \left[{[$i] \choose 1}{[$a-7] \choose [$d-7]} - {[$i] \choose 2}{[$a-14] \choose [$d-14]} + \cdots\right]`]  Subtract all the distributions for which one or more bins contain 7 or more balls.


